Test Environment for SBLIM Base Instrumentation

The SBLIM project offers a Test Suite to perform tests against
the provider implementation and consistence tests against system
values.

Prerequisites are : 

- sblim-cmpi-base package propertly installed
- testsuite package


make test
... to test the existence of a testsuite directory

make install 
... to install the input files into the corresponding testsuite
directories

make uninstall
... to delete the cmpi-base specific files out of the testsuite
directories



Run the test in the testsuite dir by executing . test-cmpi-base.sh

